spec_data.Name: lighttpd-fastcgi
spec_data.Description:
This package contains the spawn-fcgi helper for lighttpd's automatic spawning
of local FastCGI programs. Included is also a PHP .ini file to change a few
defaults needed for correct FastCGI behavior.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Mon 13 Nov 2017 11:29:30 AM EST, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: FastCGI module and spawning helper for lighttpd and PHP configuration
